<div>
<p>徽宗崇寧<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<measure quantity="11" unit="months">
<num value="11">十一</num>月</measure>
<measure quantity="23" unit="days">
<num value="23">二十三</num>日</measure>
<pc>，</pc>更定神宗徽號曰體元顯道帝德王功英文烈武欽仁聖孝皇 帝<pc>，</pc>又奉哲宗徽號曰憲元繼道<date notBefore="954" notAfter="960">顯德</date>定功欽文睿武齊聖昭孝皇帝<pc>。</pc>
<date notBefore="1107" notAfter="1110">大觀</date>元年<measure quantity="9" unit="months">
<num value="9">九</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>加上僖祖徽號為<num value="16">十六</num>字<pc>，</pc>曰立道肇基積德起功懿文憲武睿和至孝皇帝<pc>。</pc>政和<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<measure quantity="11" unit="months">
<num value="11">十一</num>月</measure>
<measure quantity="5" unit="days">
<num value="5">五</num>日</measure>
