</div>
<div>
<p>嘉定<measure quantity="13" unit="years">
<num value="13">十三</num>年</measure>
<measure quantity="10" unit="months">
<num value="10">十</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>司農寺丞嶽珂言<pc>：</pc>
<pc>“</pc>
<quote>孝宗舊諱從‘伯</quote>’從‘<quote>玉</quote>’從‘<quote>宗</quote>’<pc>。</pc>考<date notBefore="9999" notAfter="9999">國朝</date>之製<pc>，</pc>祖宗舊諱<num value="2">二</num>字者<pc>，</pc>皆著令不許並用<pc>。</pc>
